It raises its big

immediately.

Quick to anger, it

its horn to inject a powerful poison
when it becomes
agitated.

It is easily
agitated and uses
its horn for offense as soon as
it notices an
attacker.

presence, all the barbs on its back bristle up at once, and it challenges
the foe with all its might.

Nidorino dispose dune corne plus dure que du diamant.
Sil sent une prsence hostile, toutes les pointes de son dos
